==English==

===Etymology===
Named after [[w:Charles Boyle, 4th Earl of Orrery|Charles Boyle, 4th Earl of Orrery]] (1676-1731), for whom such a device was made.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/'ɒɹəɹi/}}

